events.eventDescription: GDG DevFests are large, community-run events that can offer speaker sessions across multiple product areas, all-day hack-a-thons, code labs, and more. ... GDG DevFests can be organized year round and are community run events.

WomenTechmakers powered by GDG VIT are celebrating Women in Technology on 21st March as the month of March belongs to us, women. 
The program is going to be a mix of tech and inspirational talks. Demos of Google products, quizzes etc. Eminent speakers and achievers will grace the occasion and inspire the audiences.
